{
  "stem": "9168.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- it was my intention, along with some of my other college-- I mean, high school seniors-- to go in-- who were not going into college prep courses in the university somewhere-- to go into Chicago for the secretarial course at Gregg College-- Gregg Business College-- which had a very extensive, highly-regarded court reporting course.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was never my intention to be a court reporter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't know what a court reporter was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I had a high school teacher named Ellis Alter, who always had wanted to be a court reporter.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And unbeknownst to me, he made me his alter ego while I was in college.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he knew the difficulties in our personal life, in our family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, I, of course, studied shorthand under him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he made a point of keeping me after school every day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "School ended at 3:30, and I went across the street to work on the switchboard in the hospital at 5:30 every day.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I had two hours of dead time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So he kept me after school, and he worked me up to a speed of 140 words a minute.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now, you know, at that time, secretaries were graduating from high school at 80 words a minute-- 100 if they were really good.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he got me up to that speed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't know what he had in mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew that I had enough money to go into Chicago from my mother's loan, for three months, which I did.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, of course, when I went into Chicago to register at Gregg College, I did not know what my teacher knew.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that is that the secretarial course ended at 140 words a minute.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
